<p>In a normal FireFox window it works much better.</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":35,"updated_at":"2023-01-22T23:32:10.313Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":266,"readers_count":265,"score":63.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":423814,"topic_slug":"github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update","display_username":"Jonathan L.","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":19457,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":""},"post_url":"/t/github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update/423814/6","custom_user_title":null,"reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3132024,"name":"Jonathan L.","username":"Jonathan_L","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/jonathan_l/{size}/6473_2.png","created_at":"2023-01-22T23:47:23.182Z","cooked":"<p>With github.dev you’re not limited to 60 hr per month of free usage but it gives you a very limited set of functionality</p>
<ul>
<li>A subset of syntax highlighting</li>
<li>Inability to build code or use a terminal</li>
<li>A subset of extensions</li>
</ul>
<p>The difference is github.dev runs in the client side in the browser whereas codespaces also requires a virtual machine on the server side - so costs more money for GitHub/Microsoft to run.</p>
<p>Here’s a more complete <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/codespaces/the-githubdev-web-based-editor#codespaces-and-githubdev" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">comparison of github.dev and codespaces</a>.</p>","post_number":7,"post_type":1,"posts_count":35,"updated_at":"2023-01-22T23:47:23.182Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":4,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":6,"reads":256,"readers_count":255,"score":96.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":423814,"topic_slug":"github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update","display_username":"Jonathan L.","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"https://docs.github.com/en/codespaces/the-githubdev-web-based-editor#codespaces-and-githubdev","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"The github.dev web-based editor - GitHub Docs","clicks":9}],"read":true,"user_title":"","reply_to_user":{"id":53201,"username":"tails618","name":"","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/tails618/{size}/188357_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":1}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":19457,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":""},"post_url":"/t/github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update/423814/7","custom_user_title":null,"reactions":[{"id":"heart","type":"emoji","count":1}],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":1,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3133281,"name":"Jonathan L.","username":"Jonathan_L","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/jonathan_l/{size}/6473_2.png","created_at":"2023-01-25T00:03:14.408Z","cooked":"<p>I’m not sure what the advantages or disadvantages are to the alternative Java extensions so I just changed one line to the extensions that ship with WPILib by default (including the C++ extension).</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">{
  "image": "mcr.microsoft.com/devcontainers/universal:2",
  "postCreateCommand": "cd /opt &amp;&amp; wget 'https://github.com/wpilibsuite/vscode-wpilib/releases/download/v2023.2.1/vscode-wpilib-2023.2.1.vsix'",
  "features": {
  },
  "customizations": {
    "vscode": {
      "extensions": ["/opt/vscode-wpilib-2023.2.1.vsix", "redhat.java", "vscjava.vscode-java-debug", "vscjava.vscode-java-dependency", "ms-vscode.cpptools"]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>","post_number":8,"post_type":1,"posts_count":35,"updated_at":"2023-01-25T00:03:14.408Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":217,"readers_count":216,"score":78.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":423814,"topic_slug":"github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update","display_username":"Jonathan L.","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":2}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":19457,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":""},"post_url":"/t/github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update/423814/8","custom_user_title":null,"reactions":[{"id":"heart","type":"emoji","count":2}],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":2,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3133460,"name":"","username":"nstrike","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/nstrike/{size}/167038_2.png","created_at":"2023-01-25T04:28:15.427Z","cooked":"<p>I noticed! I like the changes and put it in the repo.</p>","post_number":9,"post_type":1,"posts_count":35,"updated_at":"2023-01-25T04:28:15.427Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":8,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":183,"readers_count":182,"score":36.6,"yours":false,"topic_id":423814,"topic_slug":"github-codespaces-programming-in-your-browser-for-frc-2023-update","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair